No. 13069. Logue v. Nachtrieb et al. Decided February 4, 1913. Error to Circuit Court of Wayne county. ■ Mr. M. L. Spooner; Mr. John McSweeney and Mr. H. R. Smith, for plaintiff in error. Mr. Wayne FI art and Mr. James B. Taylor, for defendants in error. Judgment affirmed. Donahue, Wanamaker, Newman and Wilkin, JJ., concur.
